title: Discovery Build It Bigger Hurricane Proof Homes x264 720p
description: Danny travels to the Safeway Homes factory in Lexington, MS where prefabricated modular homes are built. By using an assembly line to construct the homes Safeway Homes is able to build homes very quickly. The homes turn out to be cheaper, and faster to build than a traditional house, and at the same time are resistant to a category 5 hurricane. MVGroup Forum mkv
